## Development

### Creating Libraries

```bash
# Shared TypeScript library
pnpm nx g @nx/js:lib shared/my-utils

# React library
pnpm nx g @nx/react:lib web/feature-auth

# Node library
pnpm nx g @nx/node:lib api/domain
```

### Module Boundaries

- `libs/shared/*` - Can be imported by both web and api
- `libs/web/*` - Can only be imported by web app
- `libs/api/*` - Can only be imported by api app

